The paper discusses insider threats in cybersecurity, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses the analysis, modeling, and countermeasures of insider threats, which could fall under software engineering (cs.SE), cyber-physical systems (cs.CY), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
